### POST /api/Roles/_getUserPermissions

Description: Returns the set of all PermissionFlags associated with the user.

Requirements:
- None. If the user can't be resolved, an empty array of permission flags is returned.

Effects:
- Looks up the user either by internal user ID or by kerb and returns their permission flags.

Request Body (one of):
```jsonc
// Option A: by user ID
{ "user": "<user-id>" }

// Option B: by kerb (recommended for UI calls)
{ "kerb": "<kerb>" }
```

Success Response Body (Query):
```json
[
  {
    "permissionFlags": ["string"]
  }
]
```

Error Response Body:
```json
{ "error": "string" }
```
